@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_etsorz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.exp(v1))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.84)))
    v2 = 0.10
    v0 = ((0.20 / 0.56) - (v2 / (tmp + 0.64 + v1 + 0.30)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs(0.52))
    v0 = (((v1 + 0.83 * v2 + 0.46) - (v0 + 0.98 * v2 + 0.84)) - ((v0 + 0.72 - tmp + 0.65) / v2))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
